OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police says it could
OL,8,Fface making service cuts after its #50
OL,9,Fmillion contract with data and AI
OL,10,Fcompany Palantir was blocked by the
OL,11,FMayor of London.
OL,13,FSir Sadiq Khan stepped in after he
OL,14,Fargued that the force had only engaged
OL,15,Fwith one supplier when the contract
OL,16,Fwas awarded, and the move is now
OL,17,Fsubject to a legal challenge by the
OL,18,Ftechnology giant.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
