CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,8,FMark Rowley said the process followed
OL,9,Fwas "legally and commercially
OL,10,Fcompliant".
OL,12,FIn his report for the London Policing
OL,13,FBoard, that is due to meet on
OL,14,FThursday, Sir Mark said the force
OL,15,Fcould face cutting services or staff
OL,16,Fas a result of the decision.
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FThe system to be delivered by Palantir
OL,8,Fwould have allowed the Met to cut 500
OL,9,Fjobs in response to a budget shortfall
OL,10,Fof #100 million this year and #125
OL,11,Fmillion next year, but the savings
OL,12,Fwill now have to be found elsewhere,
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,FThe budget for 2026/27 included plans
OL,16,Fto cut a total of 1,150 jobs in the
OL,17,Fforce, with the work of 500 of those
OL,18,Fto be covered by AI tools used to
OL,19,Freduce the time taken to draw up
OL,20,Fintelligence reports and analyse
OL,21,Fmobile phones.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,F"As a direct result of this decision,
OL,8,Fwe are now scoping at pace tough
OL,9,Fchoice options. While we had a
OL,10,Fcontingency list, we had not developed
OL,11,Fthis work as had hoped not to have to
OL,12,Fmake these reductions.
OL,14,F"However, we have mobilised the
OL,15,Forganisation to bring forward options.
OL,16,FThese will range from stopping
OL,17,Fservices, reducing teams or changing
OL,18,Fhow we deliver a service."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
