OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FSir Mark said that in March 2026, the
OL,13,Fnumber of Metropolitan Police Service
OL,14,F(MPS) officers per 100,000 population
OL,15,Fwas lower than at any point since 1981.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
