CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the mayor of London
OL,8,Fsaid: "The mayor fully supports the
OL,9,FMet using modern technology to drive
OL,10,Fefficiencies and improve the
OL,11,Fperformance of the police. However, as
OL,12,Fwith all procurement, we must always
OL,13,Fensure the correct processes are
OL,14,Ffollowed and that Londoners get value
OL,15,Ffor money.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,F"In this case, the Met did not present
OL,8,Fits procurement strategy for approval,
OL,9,Fas required, and the process followed
OL,10,Fby the Met did not adequately
OL,11,Fdemonstrate value for money for
OL,12,FLondoners for a proposed contract at
OL,13,Fthis value. Given the tight budgetary
OL,14,Fconstraints the police are operating
OL,15,Funder, it's even more important that
OL,16,Frobust processes are followed when
OL,17,Fawarding large contracts.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,F"The Met does face a difficult
OL,8,Ffinancial situation, which stems from
OL,9,Fthe huge cuts implemented by the
OL,10,Fprevious government and the
OL,11,Fsignificant underfunding of the Met's
OL,12,Fcapital city responsibilities.
OL,14,F"The mayor has already doubled the
OL,15,Fpolicing budget from City Hall and he
OL,16,Fwill continue to do everything he can
OL,17,Fto support the Met and secure the
OL,18,Fnational funding needed for policing
OL,19,Fin our city."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FThe report also sets out how the force
OL,8,Fis pushing for additional funding to
OL,9,Ftackle a recent wave of antisemitism
OL,10,Fthat has resulted in a series of
OL,11,Falleged arson attacks in the English
OL,12,Fcapital.
OL,14,FThe Home Office granted funding for an
OL,15,Fadditional 100 officers, but Sir Mark
OL,16,Fis pushing for an extra 300, including
OL,17,Fa dedicated team of neighbourhood and
OL,18,Farmed officers to be based permanently
OL,19,Fin north-west London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,F"This is essential if we are to
OL,8,Fprovide lasting, bespoke protection in
OL,9,Fthe face of a level of state threats
OL,10,Fand hate crime far greater than that
OL,11,Ffaced by other communities.
OL,13,F"It is not sustainable ` or
OL,14,Foperationally effective ` to rely
OL,15,Findefinitely on overtime or the
OL,16,Fredeployment of officers from across
OL,17,FLondon.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
