OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781269895
OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,F"The threat is increasing and we need
OL,8,Fa policing model capable of meeting it
OL,9,Fover the long term," the Commissioner
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"If this funding is not secured, the
OL,13,FMPS will need to reassess what is
OL,14,Faffordable in the context of a police
OL,15,Fservice already required to shrink
OL,16,Ffurther this year to balance its
OL,17,Fbudget."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@TO]tD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
