OL,3,CMet faces potential service cuts after
OL,4,C#50 million contract is blocked by
OL,5,Cmayor
OL,7,FThe force is currently using more than
OL,8,F1,000 officer shifts to protect north-
OL,9,Fwest London and other "vulnerable
OL,10,Flocations", he said.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@JO]
